file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Test anonymous operations
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /withBoth:
    get:
      security: [{}, {"apikeyScheme": []}, {"apikeyScheme2": []}]
      responses:
        200:
          description: asdadasd
  /onlyEmpty:
    get:
      security: [{}]
      responses:
        200:
          description: asdadasd
  /required:
    get:
      security: [{"apikeyScheme": []}]
      responses:
        200:
          description: asdadasd
security:
  - apikeyScheme: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    apikeyScheme:
      name: test
      type: apiKey
      in: header
    apikeyScheme2:
      name: test2
      type: apiKey
      in: header
